## 1. API Reference

| Action | Method | Endpoint | Success Code |
|--------|--------|----------|:------------:|
| Sign Up | `POST` | `auth/signup` | `201` |
| Login  | `POST` | `auth/login`  | `200` |

### Sign-Up Request

```json
{
  "username": "string",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "phone": "string",
  "password": "string"
}
```

### Login Request

```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "string"
}
```

### Success Response (both endpoints)

```json
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "data": {
    "id": 0,
    "username": "string",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "phone": "string",
    "token": "string"
  }
}
```

### Error Response (400 / 409 / 500)

```json
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "message": "string"
}
```

