## 5. Dependency Injection

### File: [lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart)

Add the following **inside** the [setup()](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart#3-34) function. Keep the Service registration **before** the Repository registration (dependency order).

```dart
import 'package:cureta/features/authentcation/data/services/auth_service.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/authentcation/data/repo/auth_repository.dart';
```

```dart
void setup() {
  // 🧱 Services
  getIt.registerSingleton<AuthService>(AuthService());

  // 📦 Repositories
  getIt.registerSingleton<AuthRepository>(
    AuthRepository(getIt.get<AuthService>()),
  );
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Remember to call [setup()](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart#3-34) inside [main()](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/main.dart#7-20) **before** `runApp()`:
> ```dart
> void main() async {
>   WidgetsFlutterBinding.ensureInitialized();
>   await DioHelper.init();
>   setup(); // ← GetIt registration
>   // ...
>   runApp(/* ... */);
> }
> ```

