|---|------|---------|
| 1 | Create `UserModel` | `data/models/user_model.dart` |
| 2 | Create `AuthResponseModel` | `data/models/auth_response_model.dart` |
| 3 | Create `AuthService` | `data/services/auth_service.dart` |
| 4 | Create `AuthRepository` | `data/repo/auth_repository.dart` |
| 5 | Register in GetIt | [core/Services/GetItServices.dart](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart) |
| 6 | Call [setup()](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/GetItServices.dart#3-34) + `DioHelper.init()` in [main()](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/main.dart#7-20) | [main.dart](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/main.dart) |
| 7 | Create `AuthViewModel` | `veiw_model/auth_view_model.dart` |
| 8 | Build Login UI | `veiw/login_screen.dart` |
| 9 | Build Sign-Up UI | `veiw/signup_screen.dart` |

